Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.95,0:00:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.10,0:00:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's my mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,First one out.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.17,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.31,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.29,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we play togeth—
