Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.21,0:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better hurry home.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The days are already getting so short.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.86,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the right way?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you fret.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This way's just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.81,0:02:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How reassuring.{lol. amazing line}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Granny, why were you out there in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.05,0:02:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Granny?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my husband!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Youkichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I cannot thank you enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.57,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't quite sure what I'd gotten myself into, to be honest.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs aren't what they used to be, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make it that far into the mountains anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.02,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't met her when you did, \NI just don't know what might have happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not have much to offer,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but please, at least rest here before you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it concerns me that she doesn't \Nknow why she ventured out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the first time. \NShe's been doing it quite a bit lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days, at dusk,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,usually when there's a beautiful sunset,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll say, "I'm going home," \Nand then she'll try to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that, in rare cases,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people start saying things \Nlike that as they get older.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.20,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as though they \Ntemporarily regress to their childhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if not consciously, she may be \Ntrying to return to her childhood home.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she and I are both \Ngetting on in years, to say the least.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that we're \Nstarting to show our age{ in all sorts of ways}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again, \Ntreating me like I've gone senile.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything untrue, did I?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I still work much harder than you, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you can't even cook rice on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do without me, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off your high horse already.{lol this couple}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate being called senile so much, \Nthen quit acting like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.18,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have company! \NDon't raise your voice in front of our guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're a mushi-shi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to have one here, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.89,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped us out when our baby had convulsions and when our rice fields became diseased.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure this will make my knee better?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.17,0:05:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... it {\i1}does{\i0} feel better.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.41,0:05:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat it again tomorrow morning, \Nand then it should be completely cured.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrific news.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginko.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Mikage.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.16,0:06:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone doesn't remember her past at all,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.23,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible for her to remember her childhood as she gets older?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say, without knowing more.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife has no memory of her past?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.59,0:06:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One day a long time ago, \Nshe just suddenly showed up in our village.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.19,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't usually cross my mind anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever I remember that day...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,honestly,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.29,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder what it was all about.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, You.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.22,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for my dad to get back from the fields first.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make sure you get home before it gets too dark, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen my daughter, Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkichi, have you seen her?{D:}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us ever saw Akane again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What village are you from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How ominous.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's the child of a demon or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying Akane was eaten by a demon?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.81,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, Akane's father volunteered to take her in.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to feel for the poor girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying so hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That new girl never comes and plays with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's no fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better quit pretending to be Akane, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I want to do this either, you know!{mfw i have no face}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dad gave it to me, so what choice do I have?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}have{\i0} to wear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Mikage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.62,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, we accepted Mikage as one of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And after some time,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.02,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,she and I were married.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We raised our children together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We grew old together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.22,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}After spending our lives with each other, \NI was sure that even our bones would be buried together{ in this village}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she started saying, "I'm going home,"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can't be so sure of that anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I must sound crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.00,0:10:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that she may remember where she's from one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.40,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If or when she does, I wonder if she'll want to go back there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.98,0:11:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At dusk, one person vanishes, and another takes his place...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.33,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of this happening before.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.49,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sometimes due to an Oomagadoki, or "Great Witching Hour" mushi,{lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which only appears in this world at dusk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who has been engulfed by it
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will appear at dusk as a shadow \Nwithout a physical body.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if someone else steps on that shadow or if the shadow steps on them,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.99,0:11:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that person will trade places with the shadow's owner, becoming engulfed by the Oomagadoki in exchange.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, that's the assumption.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,those who have appeared in such a manner have no memory of their pasts,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which means there's no real proof.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.69,0:12:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying... Akane traded places with Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what happened to Akane after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way of knowing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.49,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's possible she traded places with \Nsomeone else in the same way and is living elsewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you figure out where she may have reappeared?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.70,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that the Oomagadoki exists in a different world from ours.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.09,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can tell when and where \Nour worlds may become connected.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.07,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I hope Akane's found happiness somewhere too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm bored of this game.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play cat's cradle instead.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we play shadow tag together?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.95,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, my knee's all better.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.68,0:13:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there are others in the village who have similar problems with their legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could see to them as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.87,0:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here another night too, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I think I'll take you up on that offer.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.05,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage, I'm going to go catch some fish for Ginko.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.43,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't push yourself too hard just because your knee's better.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.33,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.72,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by evening, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird just came out of my knee!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it feels a bit better now...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about my husband—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a bruise.{rofl}{hahaha}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.37,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a big catch to—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.99,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife! She's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nowhere near sunset, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure she didn't just step out for a bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the lantern too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.93,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she finally remembered where she's from,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where... am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no one here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun is always setting here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.97,0:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So lonely...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so lonely here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.33,0:16:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet... this is that shadow's fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.23,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all because that shadow stepped on mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we play togeth—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all because that shadow stepped on mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.57,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be her?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember everything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.17,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were just going to leave without saying anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to go home that badly?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.50,0:17:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.33,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Dad and you made me truly happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.24,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't have been me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.40,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sacrificed Akane.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}wanted{\i0} to trade places with her,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so I stepped on her shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.40,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I took everything from her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I took Akane from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.01,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy too, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been happy all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.04,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.02,0:19:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to our home.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some years later,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an epidemic took Mikage's life.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's said that the two lived happily together until she passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it, Akane?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Youkichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.61,0:20:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still in that thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably couldn't step on someone else's shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.59,0:20:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You always were such a gentle, kindhearted girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.66,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I married the girl who stepped on your shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a terrible person?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate her, to this day?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.37,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please, just step on my shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane, you have to come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.11,0:21:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.93,0:21:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.32,0:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.80,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Akane!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.15,0:22:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Akane's finally come back!
